    "name": "Army Moves Overdrive",
    "steam_appid": 3295100,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/f18aeb526fbdebdd93282387f515aa4f.avif?t=1771233954\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras_big/f18aeb526fbdebdd93282387f515aa4f.avif?t=1771233954 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Army Moves Overdrive, soldier. If you thought the original was tough, get ready for this new version to make you sweat blood. Shape up or you'll end up minced meat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aimed at modern players but with full respect for the original, in this thrilling action story we take control of the members of S.M.A.S.H., an agency dedicated to counter-developing super-advanced weaponry created by the Wunderwaffe—an evil organization capable of altering the course of World War II.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features that'll leave you breathless:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay variety</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go from driving like a maniac to dishing out beatdowns on foot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/335645dbaa41f1cb224fa1b87a6917b7.poster.avif?t=1771233954\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/335645dbaa41f1cb224fa1b87a6917b7.webm?t=1771233954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/335645dbaa41f1cb224fa1b87a6917b7.mp4?t=1771233954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An arsenal that'll blow your mind </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a variety of weapons that would make Rambo himself green with envy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/db93b50c4c871573e20d8c59aaae26a1.poster.avif?t=1771233954\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/db93b50c4c871573e20d8c59aaae26a1.webm?t=1771233954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/db93b50c4c871573e20d8c59aaae26a1.mp4?t=1771233954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Vehicles galore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master jeeps, helicopters, airplanes, and any contraption that moves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/73456252a92886144a42244a3e685108.poster.avif?t=1771233954\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/73456252a92886144a42244a3e685108.webm?t=1771233954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/73456252a92886144a42244a3e685108.mp4?t=1771233954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enemies scarier than a Monday out of whiskey</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against soldiers, tanks, and final bosses that'll make you wish you'd chosen to be an accountant.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/5f4ac40a39e361a11ec9d4f6d0ff0aeb.poster.avif?t=1771233954\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/5f4ac40a39e361a11ec9d4f6d0ff0aeb.webm?t=1771233954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/5f4ac40a39e361a11ec9d4f6d0ff0aeb.mp4?t=1771233954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Brazen artistic style</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A visual explosion so powerful it'll make you wonder if you need new glasses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/90cce3c8ffcf95cf62616b45b56e873f.poster.avif?t=1771233954\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/90cce3c8ffcf95cf62616b45b56e873f.webm?t=1771233954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/90cce3c8ffcf95cf62616b45b56e873f.mp4?t=1771233954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An epic war symphony</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive headfirst into the action with music that'll make you smell napalm in the morning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Army Moves Overdrive</strong> is for the brave only, whether you're a hardened veteran or a rookie itching for war. With controls even a boomer could handle and an addictive difficulty, each mission will have you gripping the controller like your life depends on it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes, or would you rather go back to playing Candy Crush? The battle awaits you in <strong>Army Moves Overdrive</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/9ea8a120e48f298fb814bacb00c69e78.poster.avif?t=1771233954\" width=640 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/9ea8a120e48f298fb814bacb00c69e78.webm?t=1771233954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295100/extras/9ea8a120e48f298fb814bacb00c69e78.mp4?t=1771233954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
